==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Ten-strike
<hw>Ten"-strike`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn>
<fld>(Tenpins)</fld> <def>A knocking down of all ten pins at one
delivery of the ball<-- also, strike-->.</def> <mark>[U. S.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Any quick, decisive stroke or act.</def>
<mark>[Colloq. U. S.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Tensure</ent>⟦br⟧
